- See you later, Les

49:41.849 --> 49:43.849
Ella. Les will be
back in a minute

49:45.649 --> 49:48.049
He's always late

49:52.949 --> 49:55.349
You scared now?

50:40.449 --> 50:42.649
Do you think he knows?

50:45.049 --> 50:47.249
Of course he does

51:11.399 --> 51:13.799
How long he's been out there?

51:14.999 --> 51:17.349
He must come down and see us

51:21.149 --> 51:22.949
What can we do?

51:23.899 --> 51:26.149
It depends on him really

51:27.799 --> 51:30.349
Why it only depends on him?

51:31.399 --> 51:33.749
There's... anyhow

