He surveys the boat as
if it prepared judgment

51:36.199 --> 51:38.299
It's just his way of
knowing we're there

51:38.334 --> 51:40.149
Yes, he's done that

51:48.199 --> 51:50.649
You're just gonna lie here?

51:51.249 --> 51:54.899
There's no hurry.
I finish my cigarette.

52:57.949 --> 52:59.749
I'm sorry, Les

53:01.899 --> 53:04.149
It just happened

53:04.999 --> 53:07.399
There's nothing
personal against you

53:10.299 --> 53:12.999
I just kick you fucking head

53:14.899 --> 53:18.699
I won't fight you, Les. Hit me if
you think it'll make you feel better

53:24.949 --> 53:27.649
What about my son?

53:28.649 --> 53:32.099
What do you think happens to my
son when you are fucking my wife?

53:32.134 --> 53:34.749
- It wasn't like that
- Like what, Joe?

53:36.349 --> 53:38.199
Tell me what it was like

53:40.699 --> 53:42.449
Look, I'll get my stuff

53:42.649 --> 53:46.599
- I leave you to sort it out with Ella.
- This hard fucking barge!

53:50.249 --> 53:52.499
I'll go

54:03.749 --> 54:05.949
So he'll write me a letter?

54:08.149 --> 54:10.299
That's what he said

54:10.399 --> 54:12.399
Do you want a cup of tea?

54:12.799 --> 54:15.699
- Right, I'll do this one
- Me too

54:18.749 --> 54:21.199
Look what we said before
to each other, Joe.

55:59.149 --> 56:00.649
Stop!

56:00.749 --> 56:02.549
Stop! I don't like it. Joe

56:03.349 --> 56:05.849
I can't swim.
You know it. Stop!

56:06.249 --> 56:09.399
I'm scared, I'm
scared, bastard

56:35.649 --> 56:38.349
They've set the
date for that man's trial

56:53.649 --> 56:56.149
FATHER OF TWO TO STAND TRIAL

56:57.399 --> 56:59.199
I thought 4 he has

56:59.299 --> 57:02.799
- What?
- Children. 4 kids

57:03.249 --> 57:05.399
Yes, so did I. It
must be a mistake

57:07.049 --> 57:09.899
Push out the paper

57:14.449 --> 57:16.099
Poor bastard

57:16.299 --> 57:18.614
How? He killed
an innocent woman

57:18.649 --> 57:21.199
You are not the
judge, he didn't do it

57:21.234 --> 57:23.199
What makes you say it?

57:24.099 --> 57:27.199
- It was an accident
- Not what they think

57:27.599 --> 57:30.099
She died without her clothes
so it must be a murder?

57:30.449 --> 57:33.849
Do you want to know how
I know it was an accident?

57:33.899 --> 57:35.949
I thought you were not
interested in all that

57:39.449 --> 57:41.099
I know

59:16.599 --> 59:18.499
I came for my stuff

59:18.799 --> 59:19.949
I'll get it

59:30.649 --> 59:33.149
- How is Jim?
- You know how he is

59:33.399 --> 59:35.299
Go and see him yourself

59:36.399 --> 59:40.299
I thought he was coming
Stay with me for a while

59:51.349 --> 59:54.049
- You want a cup of tea?
- You've got work to do

01:00:01.049 --> 01:00:03.599
They asked me as a
witness at the trial

01:00:04.199 --> 01:00:06.049
One of us is enough

01:00:06.749 --> 01:00:09.799
I cannot tell
them anymore anyway

01:00:12.999 --> 01:00:16.649
- You'll say hello to the boy for me?
- Go and see him

